# Spec Edit Safety Rule

Requirement specifications under `spec/requirements/` are user-owned artifacts.

- Do not create, modify, rename, move, or delete files in `spec/requirements/` unless explicitly requested.
- If implementation work implies a spec update, ask first unless the user explicitly requested a spec edit.
- Treat manual user edits in `spec/requirements/` as source of truth.
- Never silently overwrite user wording; ask on conflicts.
